Jun 27 2005	A+ service	Our week at the Jockey Club was excellent. I am not used to having daily maid service with a time share program. Being there in the heat of the summer meant that the 3 of us were sometimes taking two showers a day. The cleaning service kept up with clean towels daily and plenty of them. They also arrange for a full cleaning mid-week, free of charge. The front desk was extrememly helpful. They provided us with a taxi service from the front door to the airport - which was much appreciated. Even though you can walk around to the Bellagio and get a ride from there, we spared ourselves the heat and stayed in the A/C until our ride arrived. You'll be a little taken back with the fact that the facility is located in a parking lot when everyone else has filled their available space with greenery. But don't let that stop you from booking a reservation. Really, really a great deal.	
